stories.title: Rain and Gayle lash India
stories.summary:
The Queen's Park Oval at Trinidad might be one of India's favourite
away grounds but that did not save them from a thrashing at the hands
of the West Indians on Saturday

stories.title: Gayle leads West Indies to exciting triumph
stories.summary: The day began in a moment of solemn silence and ended in a dramatic eruption of joy at the Queen's Park Oval in Trinidad
